","tag-jihad","tag-mecca-makkah","tag-obligations-faraid","tag-travel-al-safr","tag-lesser-pilgrimage-umrah","tag-war-al-harb","tag-women-al-nisa"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9vP","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":6563,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/17\/best-jihad-women-hajj-umrah\/","url_meta":{"origin":36569,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Best jihad for women is Hajj pilgrimage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, shall we not attend the military expeditions and fight in jihad alongside you?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo, rather the best and most beautiful jihad for you is the Hajj, a blessed pilgrimage.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1861\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6565,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/17\/jihad-hajj-mabrur-best-iman\/","url_meta":{"origin":36569,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Struggle: Jihad, Hajj among best deeds after faith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was asked, \u201cWhat is the best deed?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cFaith in Allah and His Messenger.\" It was said, \u201cThen what?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cJihad in the way\u00a0of Allah.\u201d It was said, \u201cThen what?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cA blessed\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23706,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/09\/07\/hajj-o-allah-forgive-pilgrims\/","url_meta":{"origin":36569,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Forgive pilgrims, those they supplicate for","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 7, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, forgive the pilgrims and those for whom the pilgrims seek forgiveness.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 8818 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15508,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/29\/go-to-hajj-with-wife\/","url_meta":{"origin":36569,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Go perform pilgrimage with your wife","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA man should not be alone with a woman, nor shou